title: Newark Elks Bowling League announces high scores
text: Newark Elks Bowling League announces high scores Comment Posted Oct. 16, 2015 at 3:42 PM Updated at 3:42 PM Posted Oct. 16, 2015 at 3:42 PM Wayne, N.Y. The Newark Elks Bowling League announced its high scores for the week of Oct. 12. The scratch game high scores include Todd Brockhuizen (269), Derrick DeWind (258), Ed Fenyn (262), Abe Hara (276), Sax Heidenreich (268), Jack Howell (270), Larry Marker (278), Mike Means (268), Gary Miller (300) and Roger Salamone (256). The scratch series high scores include Jim Batterby (698), Todd Brockhuizen (731), Ryan Davis (702), Derrick DeWind (715), Abe Hara (711), Jack Howell (753), Mike Means (697), Gary Miller (790), Erik Pentycofe (672) and Roger Salamone (673). Wayne Post
